; Test expr directive via general_directive
; Exercise the expr keyword (alias for eval) through the switch

expr 1 + 1

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
